snippet.title: The Lord of the Rings: Rise to War - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
So it begins. Make ready, Tacticians, for The Lord of the Rings: Rise to War. The game will be officially launched on 23rd of September, 2021 in Europe, America, Oceania and Southeast Asia. Stay tuned!
Pre-register your place in the battle today: https://www.lotr-risetowar.com

#IGN #TheLordoftheRings
